item.title: Stack
item.description: Use case Computer use stack internally called the call stack. The example of [function call] Actions Push: Add a new item to the top Pop: Remove the topmost item and read it repl example function Stack(){ let items = []; this.push = function(item){ items.push(item); } this.pop = function(){ return items.pop(); } this.peek = function(){ return items[items.length-1]; } this.isEmpty = function(){ return items.length ==0; } this.clear = function(){ items = []; } this.
